column1: Disclaimer: This file contains trip information collected to produce the Safety Score. Each record represents a trip. Trips on service mode or less than 0.1 miles in length are excluded as they are not included in the Safety Score calculation.
For more information about the Safety Score please refer to the support page: https://www.tesla.com/support/safety-score

column4: Miles driven on the trip while not using Autopilot
column5: Seconds following with 1 second excluding Autopilot driving
column6: Seconds following within 3 seconds excluding Autopilot driving
column8: Seconds experiencing longitudinal acceleration less than of -0.3g excluding Autopilot driving
column9: Seconds experiencing longitudinal acceleration less than of -0.1g excluding Autopilot driving
column11: Seconds experiencing lateral acceleration greater than 0.4g or less than -0.4g excluding Autopilot driving
column12: Seconds experiencing lateral acceleration greater than 0.2g or less than -0.2g excluding Autopilot driving
column14: Count of Forward Collision Warnings on the trip excluding warnings occurring while driving on Autopilot
column15: Count of Forced Autopilot Disengagements on the trip
